 * DEALINGS IN THE SOFTWARE.
 *
 * Author:
 *   Gareth Hughes <gareth@@valinux.com>
 *   Kevin E. Martin <martin@@valinux.com>
 *
 * Converted to common header format:
 *   Jens Owen <jens@@tungstengraphics.com>
